Package: rblncr
Title: Automatically Rebalance Equity Portfolios
Version: 0.9.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Riaz",
           family = "Arbi",
           email = "riazarbi@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package allows users to create model portfolios (which are desired percentage weights of assets in an equity portfolio) and to apply these models to supported backends. The wrapper function `balance_portfolio` will submit trades to the backend until the reported holdings are within the specified weight tolerances of the model portoflio.
